author: The Current
description:
Watch Brigitte Calls Me Baby perform "I'm Still Here" live at Surly Brewing Co., Minneapolis
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Fronted by charismatic vocalist Wes Leavins, the Chicago band Brigitte Calls Me Baby performed a more than 30-minute set at Surly Brewing Company in Minneapolis on July 13, 2023, as part of The Current Happy Hours series. 

Watch a performance of "I'm Still Here" above.

Musicians
Jeremy Benshish – drums
Jack Fluegel – guitar
Wes Leavins – vocals
Trevor Lynch – guitar
Devin Wessels – bass

description:

title: Your Smith shares what it's like to perform pregnant
